Run spark:
1. go to: /Users/alon_ss/Learning/Recommender/spark-1.6.1-bin-hadoop2.6
2. "./bin/spark-shell --master local[2]" // run spark with 2 nodes
3. localhost:4040/jobs

Connect to Server:
1. go to: cd /usr/local/etc/openssl/
2. RUN: sudo ssh -i intooiTV.pem ec2-user@ec2-52-33-215-84.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com

tomcat:
sudo service tomcat8 stop
sudo service tomcat8 start

mongo:
1. mongod --dbpath /var/lib/mongo/data/db
sudo service mongod stop
sudo service mongod start


copy to server:
1. go to: cd /usr/local/etc/openssl/
2. sudo scp -i intooiTV.pem  /Users/alon_ss/Learning/Recommender/simpleServer/target/ServerSide.war ec2-user@ec2-52-33-215-84.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com:ServerSide.war
ยง3. sudo ssh -i intooiTV.pem ec2-user@ec2-52-33-215-84.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com
4. sudo rm -rf /usr/share/tomcat8/webapps/ServerSide
5. sudo rm -rf /usr/share/tomcat8/webapps/ServerSide.war
6. sudo cp ServerSide.war /usr/share/tomcat8/webapps/ServerSide.war
7. sudo service tomcat8 stop
8. sudo service tomcat8 start
9. sudo vi /usr/share/tomcat8/webapps/ServerSide/WEB-INF/classes/application.properties
10. sudo service tomcat8 stop
11. sudo service tomcat8 start
12. delete USER index from mongo  - its a bug!!!


copy client:
